# Nest wiring

## Modules
- `HttpModule` (`driving/nest/http/`), `SqsModule` (`driving/nest/sqs/`).
- `DrizzlePersistenceModule` (`driven/drizzle/`), `EventBridgeModule` (`driven/eventbridge/`).
- HTTP clients: `FeatureFlagModule`, etc. in `driven/http/*/`.

## Injection
- Inject ports (e.g. `EnrollmentServicePort`, `EnrollmentRepositoryPort`) via `@Injectable()` adapters.
- Use `@InjectDb()` for Drizzle in `src/driven/drizzle/drizzle.provider.ts`.

## Entry points
- `main.api.ts` — HTTP API. `main.worker.ts` — SQS worker.
